t("Savior of the damsels in distress", "迷路少女拯救者")
t("Saved Melinda from her terrible fate in the Crypt of Kryl-Feijan.", "从卡洛·斐济邪教手中把梅琳达从厄运中拯救出来。")
t("Impossible Death", "不可能的死亡")
t("Got killed by your future self.", "被未来的自己杀死。")
t("Self-killer", "自杀者")
t("Killed your future self.", "杀死未来的自己。")
