t("Used the Sher'Tul fortress exploratory farportal at least 7 times with the same character.", "同一角色通关夏·图尔堡垒的随机迷宫7次以上。")
t("Orbituary", "轨道学者")
t("Stabilized the Abashed Expanse to maintain it in orbit.", "控制次元浮岛使其稳定在轨道上。")
t("Wibbly Wobbly Timey Wimey Stuff", "摇晃的不稳定法杖")
t("Killed the weaver queen and the temporal defiler.", "杀死编织者女皇和时空污秽魔。")
t("Matrix style!", "黑客帝国！")
t("Finished the whole Abashed Expanse zone without being hit by a single void blast or manaworm. Dodging's fun!", "探索完整个次元浮岛并且毫发无损。我闪！")
t("The Right thing to do", "正确的选择")
t("Did the righteous thing in the ring of blood and disposed of the Blood Master.", "你在血色之环做出了正确的选择并处置了血色领主。")
t("Thralless", "奴隶救星！")
t("Freed at least 30 enthralled slaves in the slavers' compound.", "在奴隶营解救至少30名奴隶。")
t("Lost in translation", "迷失")
t("Destroyed the naga portal in the slazish fens and got caught in the after-effect.", "在斯拉伊什沼泽摧毁娜迦传送门，并被带回旧大陆。")
t("Dreaming my dreams", "我的梦就是你的梦")
