section "game/modules/tome/data/birth/classes/afflicted.lua"

t("Afflicted", "痛苦系")
t("Some walk in shadow, alone, unloved, unwanted. What powers they wield may be mighty, but their names are forever cursed.", "他们是一群漫步于阴影中、孤独的、讨人厌的、被遗弃的人。他们的力量或许很强大，但他们的名字永远被诅咒着。")
t("Afflicted classes have been twisted by their association with evil forces.", "痛苦系因为他们使用了邪恶的力量而变得扭曲。")
t("They can use these forces to their advantage, but at a cost...", "他们能将这股力量转化为优势，但会为此付出一定的代价……")
t("Cursed", "被诅咒者")
t("Affliction can run to the soul, and hatred can fill one's entire being. Overcome someone else's hated curse to know its dreaded meaning.", "诅咒可以深入灵魂，使某人充满憎恨。战胜另外一个人的憎恨诅咒来领会这种可怕的力量。")
t("Through ignorance, greed or folly the Cursed served some dark design and are now doomed to pay for their sins.", "被诅咒者曾经因为无知、贪婪或者愚昧，服从于黑暗的指示。现在，他们因罪恶而身受灾难折磨。")
t("Their only master now is the hatred they carry for every living thing.", "他们现在唯一的主人，是对那些生者心中的憎恨。")
t("Drawing strength from the death of all they encounter, the Cursed become terrifying combatants.", "他们从他们遇到的死亡中吸取力量，成为恐怖的战士。")
t("Worse, any who approach the Cursed can be driven mad by their terrible aura.", "更可怕的是，任何接近被诅咒者的人，会受可怕光环的影响而发狂。")
t("Their most important stats are: Strength and Willpower", "他们最重要的属性是：力量和意志。")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +5 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +0 体质")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +4 Willpower, +0 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +4 意志 , +0 灵巧")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +2", "#GOLD# 每等级生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +2")
t("Doomed", "末日使者")
t("In shaded places in unknown lands thou must overcome thyself and see thy doom.", "在遥远大陆的一个一男的地方，你必须战胜你自己并看到你自己的末日。")
t("The Doomed are fallen mages who once wielded powerful magic wrought by ambition and dark bargains.", "末日使者是一些堕落的法师，他们曾经由于野心，通过黑暗的契约，获得了强大的魔法。")
t("Stripped of their magic by the dark forces that once served them, they have learned to harness the hatred that burns in their minds.", "被黑暗剥夺了魔法力量的他们，开始学习如何驱使他们心头燃烧的憎恨的力量。")
t("Only time will tell if they can choose a new path or are doomed forever.", "只有时间会证明他们是选择了一条新的道路还是一条永远的末日惩罚之路。")
t("The Doomed strike from behind a veil of darkness or a host of shadows.", "末日使者操纵阴影，从黑暗中发动攻击。")
t("They feed upon their enemies as they unleash their minds on all who confront them.", "他们可以汲取敌人的灵魂，并对所有面对它的人的精神施加惩罚")
t("Their most important stats are: Willpower and Cunning", "他们最重要的属性是：意志和灵巧。")
t("#GOLD#Stat modifiers:", "#GOLD# 属性修正：")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +0 体质")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Magic, +4 Willpower, +5 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 魔法 , +4 意志 , +5 灵巧")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +0", "#GOLD# 每等级生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +0")


