section "game/modules/tome/data/birth/classes/corrupted.lua"

t("Defiler", "堕落系")
t("Dark thoughts, black bloods, vile deeds... Those who spill their brethren's blood will find its power.", "黑暗的思想、黑色的血液、卑鄙的行为……那些背信弃义的人会发现他们的力量所在。")
t("Defilers are touched by the mark of evil. They are a blight on the world. Working to promote the cause of evil, they serve their masters, or themselves become masters.", "堕落者身上有邪恶的印记，他们是世界的祸害，服务于他们的邪恶主人，或者他们自己成为主人。")
t("Reaver", "收割者")
t("Reap thee the souls of thine enemies, and the powers of darkness shall enter thy flesh.", "收割敌人的灵魂，你会发现黑暗的力量涌入体内。")
t("Reavers are terrible foes, charging their enemies with a weapon in each hand.", "收割者是一个恐怖的对手，他可以向敌人挥舞两把单手武器。")
t("They can harness the blight of evil, infecting their foes with terrible contagious diseases while crushing their skulls with devastating combat techniques.", "他们可以驾驭邪恶的枯萎术，将恐怖的疾病传染给目标，然后击碎他们的头颅。")
t("Their most important stats are: Strength and Magic", "他们最重要的属性是：力量和魔法。")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +4 Strength, +1 Dexterity, +0 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +4 力量 , +1 敏捷 , +0 体质")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +4 Magic, +0 Willpower, +0 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +4 魔法 , +0 意志 , +0 灵巧")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +2", "#GOLD# 每等级生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +2")
t("Corruptor", "堕落者")
t("Blight and depravity hold the greatest powers. Accept temptation and become one with corruption.", "枯萎和邪恶掌握了强大的力量。接受诱惑成为堕落者中的一员吧。")
t("A corruptor is a terrible foe, wielding dark magics that can sap the very soul of her target.", "堕落者是一个恐怖的对手，使用黑暗魔法并汲取目标的灵魂。")
t("They can harness the blight of evil, crushing souls, stealing life force to replenish themselves.", "他们驾驭邪恶的枯萎术，粉碎灵魂，偷取生命力量来治疗自己。")
t("The most powerful corruptors can even take on some demonic aspects for themselves.", "最强大的堕落者甚至可以掌握恶魔的力量。")
t("Their most important stats are: Magic and Willpower", "他们最重要的属性是：魔法和意志。")
t("#GOLD#Stat modifiers:", "#GOLD# 属性修正：")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 Strength, +0 Dexterity, +2 Constitution", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +0 力量 , +0 敏捷 , +2 体质")
t("#LIGHT_BLUE# * +4 Magic, +3 Willpower, +0 Cunning", "#LIGHT_BLUE# * +4 魔法 , +3 意志 , +0 灵巧")
t("#GOLD#Life per level:#LIGHT_BLUE# +0", "#GOLD# 每等级生命加值： #LIGHT_BLUE# +0")


