section "game/modules/tome/data/birth/classes/tutorial.lua"

t("Tutorial Adventurer", "探索模式冒险家")
t("Adventurers have a generic talent set to teach to young ones.", "冒险家们有一套通用的理论可以传授给菜鸟们。")


