t("Skeletons are animated bones, undead creatures both strong and dexterous.", "骷髅是由有灵性的骨头组成的强壮而敏捷的不死生物。")
t("They have access to #GOLD#special skeleton talents#WHITE# and a wide range of undead abilities:", "它们天生具有独特的 #GOLD# 骷髅 #WHITE# 技能和一系列不死系技能：")
