section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/elisa-orb-scrying.lua"

t("You immerse your mind in the Way and let knowledge flow in.", "你专注你的意志与维网取得链接，使信息传输进来。")
t("[You do not gain any knowledge.]", "[你没有获得任何信息。]")
t("You pause and recall past memories.", "你停了下来，开始回忆过去。")
t("[Images and knowledge flow in.]", "[图像和知识涌现了出来。]")
t("[You do not recognize anything new.]", "[你没想起什么新东西。]")
t("Oh, hi @playername@, have you got something new to show me?", "啊，你好 @playername@ ，有什么新东西给我看么？")
t("Yes, Elisa, could you have a look at these objects please? [show her the items the orb could not identify]", "是的，埃莉萨，你能帮我看看这个物品么？[给她看看水晶球无法辨识的物品。]")
t("Err, no... sorry, I just wanted to hear a friendly voice.", "呃，没有……抱歉，我只想听听你甜美的声音。")
t("Not yet sorry!", "没事，抱歉！")
t([[#LIGHT_GREEN#*You hear something akin to a muffled giggle*#WHITE#
Oh, you are #{bold}#SOOOO#{normal}# cute!]], [[#LIGHT_GREEN#*你听到捂着嘴巴咯咯笑的声音*#WHITE#
呵，你实在#{bold}#太……#{normal}# 可爱了！]])
t("Goodbye, Elisa!", "再见，埃莉萨！")


