section "game/modules/tome/data/chats/shadow-crypt-yeek-clone.lua"

t("No time to talk fellow Wayist! ATTACK! FOR THE WAY!", "没时间闲聊了，我的同胞！冲啊！为了维网！")
t("[leave]", "[离开]")
t("The foolish cultist that created me is no more. What am I to do now...", "那个创造了我的愚蠢邪教徒已经死了。我现在应该做什么呢…")
t("You are me, come with me!", "你就是我，和我一起走吧！")
t("You should head back to Irkkk.", "你应该回伊尔克去。")
t("I fear that would get confusing very fast. I think I will go back to Irkkk. Farewell my clone!", "我担心这样会让我很困惑的。我觉得我应该回伊尔克去。再见了，我的克隆！")
t("Sure... if you prefer to think about it this way. We are all part of The Way anyway.", "啊……如果你愿意这么想也没问题。反正，我们都是维网的一份子。")
t("I think so too, farewell my clone.", "我也是这么想的，再见了，我的克隆。")
t("Clone? No you are the clone.", "克隆？不，你是我的克隆。")
t("Farewell.", "再见。")


