t("A drake hatchling; not too powerful by itself, but it usually comes with its brothers and sisters.", "一只幼龙。它本身并不强大，但是它们经常集体行动。")
t("fire drake", "火龙")
t("A mature fire drake, armed with deadly breath and nasty claws.", "一只成年火龙，拥有炽烈的火焰吐息和锋利的爪子。")
t("fire wyrm", "火焰巨龙")
t("An old and powerful fire drake, armed with deadly breath and nasty claws.", "一只年长且强大的火龙，拥有炽烈的火焰吐息和锋利的爪子。")


