section "game/modules/tome/data/general/objects/brotherhood-artifacts.lua"

t("Elixir of the Fox", "狡诈药剂")
t("A vial of pink, airy fluid.", "一瓶粉红色的透明液体。")
t("permanently increase your dexterity and cunning by three", "永久提升你3点敏捷与灵巧点数")
t("#00FF00#The elixir has given you foxlike physical and mental agility!", "#00FF00#药剂给予了你狐狸般的物理、精神能力！")
t("Elixir of Avoidance", "闪避药剂")
t("A vial of opaque green fluid.", "一瓶浑浊的绿色液体。")
t("permanently increase your defense and ranged defense by six", "永久提升你6点近身和远程闪避")
t("#00FF00#The elixir has improved your defensive instincts!", "#00FF00#药剂提高了你的防御本能！")
t("Elixir of Precision", "精准药剂")
t("A vial of chunky red fluid.", "一瓶粘稠的红色液体。")
t("permanently increase your physical critical strike chance by 4%", "永久提升你4%物理暴击率")
t("#00FF00#The elixir has improved your eye for an enemy's weak points!", "#00FF00#药剂提高了你发现敌人弱点的能力！")
t("Elixir of Mysticism", "神秘药剂")
t("A vial of glowing cyan fluid.", "一瓶炽热的青色液体。")
t("permanently increase your magic and willpower by three", "永久提升你3点魔法和意志点数")
t("#00FF00#The elixir has augmented your magical and mental capacity!", "#00FF00#药剂增加了你的魔法和精神能量！")
t("Elixir of the Savior", "守护药剂")
t("A vial of bubbling, slate-colored fluid.", "一瓶翻滚着泡沫的灰色液体。")
t("permanently increase all your saving throws by 4", "永久提升你4点全体豁免")
t("#00FF00#The elixir has improved your resistance to unpleasant effects!", "#00FF00#药剂增加了你抵抗不良效果的能力！")
t("Elixir of Mastery", "掌握药剂")
t("A vial of thick maroon fluid.", "一瓶浓郁的栗色液体。")
t("grant you four additional stat points", "获得4点额外属性点数")
t("#00FF00#The elixir has greatly expanded your capacity for improving your mind and body.", "#00FF00#药剂大大提升了你的智力和体能。")
t("You have %d stat point(s) to spend. Press G to use them.", "你有%d属性点。请按G使用。")
t("Elixir of Explosive Force", "爆炸药剂")
t("A vial of churning orange fluid.", "一瓶浑浊的橙色液体。")
t("permanently increase your chance to critically strike with spells by 4%", "永久提升你4%法术暴击率")
t("#00FF00#The elixir has improved your eye for an enemy's magical weak points!", "#00FF00#药剂提升了你发现敌人魔法弱点的能力！")
t("Elixir of Serendipity", "幸运药剂")
t("A vial of lively yellow fluid.", "一瓶流动的黄色液体。")
t("permanently increase your luck by 5", "永久提升你5点运气")
t("#00FF00#The elixir seems to have subtly repositioned your entire being within the fabric of reality!", "#00FF00#这瓶炼金药剂似乎完全改变了你的整个人生！")
t("Elixir of Focus", "专注药剂")
t("A vial of clear, steaming fluid.", "一瓶透明的沸腾液体。")
t("grant you two additional class talent points", "获得额外2点职业技能点数")
t("Elixir of Brawn", "蛮牛药剂")
t("A vial of sluggish tan fluid.", "一瓶粘稠的棕褐色液体。")
t("permanently increase your strength and constitution by three", "永久提升你3点力量和体质点数")
t("#00FF00#The elixir has augmented your physical might and resilience!", "#00FF00#药剂提升了你物理打击能力和抵抗力！")
t("Elixir of Stoneskin", "石肤药剂")
t("A vial of grainy, iron-colored fluid.", "一瓶带有特殊纹理、泛着金属光泽的液体。")
t("permanently increase your armor by four", "永久提升你4点护甲值")
t("#00FF00#The elixir has reinforced your entire body!", "#00FF00#药剂重组了你整个身体！")
t("Elixir of Foundations", "领悟药剂")
t("A vial of murky white fluid.", "一瓶朦胧的白色液体。")
t("grant you two additional generic talent points", "获得额外2点通用技能点数")
t("#00FFFF#You drink the elixir and feel forever transformed!", "#00FFFF#你喝下了药剂，你感受到你的身体发生了永久性的变化！")
t("#00FF00#The elixir has improved your capacity for exercising your core talents.", "#00FF00#药剂提升了你核心技能的能力！")
t("Taint of Purging", "堕落印记：清除")
t("Infusion of Wild Growth", "纹身：根须缠绕")
t("cloudy, heavy emerald", "半透明的厚重翡翠")
t("Lifebinding Emerald", "生命之心")
t("green", "绿宝石")
t("A lopsided, heavy emerald with murky green clouds shifting sluggishly under the surface.", "一块不规则的厚重翡翠，表面有云纹浮动。")
t("potion", "药水")
