t("orb", "水晶球")
t("orb of scrying", "鉴定水晶球")
t("Scrying Orb", "鉴定水晶球")
t("This orb will automatically identify items you find.", "这个球是半身人先知埃莉萨给你的，它会自动为你鉴定装备。")
t("unstable rod", "不稳定的魔杖")
t([[This rod is made entirely of voratun, infused with raw magical energies that can bend space itself.
You have heard of such items before. They are very useful to adventurers, allowing faster travel.]], "这个法杖通体用沃瑞钽打造，充满了可以撕裂空间的奥术能量。你以前曾听说过此类物品。它们对于冒险者的快速旅行非常有帮助。")
t("recall the user to the worldmap after 40 turns", "传送至世界地图（等待40回合）")
t("Force a recall", "强制使用回归之杖")
t("The Fortress Shadow warned you that trying to force a recall without finding the portal back could break the exploratory farportal forever.", "堡垒之影警告你，如果在没有找到返回传送门的情况下尝试强行召回，可能会永久破坏远古探索传送门。")
t("Space around you starts to dissolve...", "你周围的空间开始消解...")
t("Cancel", "取消")
t("Recall", "启动回归之杖")
t("The rod emits a strange noise, glows briefly and returns to normal.", "法杖发出奇怪的响声，闪了下光又恢复了正常。")
