t("Crafted for a warlord who wanted to keep his subjects under a stralite grip. Dark thoughts went into the making of these gauntlets, literally.", "一个军阀为了永远掌握他的臣民而制造的.黑暗的思想被真正的灌注进去这些手套里.")
t("Icy Kill", "冰冷杀戮")
