树木深深地扎根在土地上……#{normal}#]])
t([[There is an inscription here:
#{italic}#...The eldritch force burns all that lives.#{normal}#]], [[这里有一段提示：
#{italic}#……可怕的力量燃烬一切生命#{normal}#]])
t([[There is an inscription here:
#{italic}#Darkness beyond twilight.
Crimson from the blood that flows...#{normal}#]], [[这里有一段提示:
