section "game/modules/tome/data/quests/staff-absorption.lua"

t("A mysterious staff", "奇怪的法杖")
t("Deep in the Dreadfell you fought and destroyed the Master, a powerful vampire.", " 在恐惧王座深处你和一个强大的吸血鬼大法师战斗并杀死了他。")
t("They asked about the staff.", " 他们想抢走法杖。")
t("On your way out of the Dreadfell you were ambushed by a band of orcs and left for dead.", " 当你走出恐惧王座的时候你受到了一队兽人小队的偷袭，他们把你干掉了。")
