t("#SLATE#* You must explore the ruins of Kor'Pul and find out what lurks there and what treasures are to be gained!#WHITE#", "#SLATE#* 你必须进入卡·普尔废墟去调查那里潜伏着什么怪物并找到那里的宝藏！#WHITE#")


