t("Gnashing Teeth", "咬牙切齿")
t("@Source@ tries to bite @Target@ with razor sharp teeth!", "@Source@ 尝试用尖锐的牙齿咬 @Target@ ！")
t("The scent of blood sends the %ss into a frenzy!", "鲜血的气味使得%s们变得狂热！")
