t("Bleed", "流血")
t("Inflicts a 10-turn bleed effect.", "制造 10 回合的流血效果。")
t("Confusion", "混乱")
t("Use your mental powers to confuse the target for five turns.", "使用你的精神力量使目标混乱 5 回合。.")


