section "game/modules/tome/data/talents/spells/golemancy.lua"

t("Your golem is out of sight; you cannot establish direct control.", "你的傀儡在视线外，你无法直接控制它。")
t("Interact with the Golem", "检查傀儡")
t([[Interact with your golem to check its inventory, talents, ...
		Note: You can also do that while taking direct control of the golem.]], "和你的傀儡交互，检查它的物品、技能等。")
t("Refit Golem", "改装傀儡")
t("You have been interrupted!", "你被打断！")
t("You need to ready 2 alchemist gems in your quiver to heal your golem.", "你至少在你的弹药栏内装备2枚炼金宝石，才能够修理你的傀儡。")
t("You need to ready 15 alchemist gems in your quiver to heal your golem.", "你至少在你的弹药栏内装备15枚炼金宝石，才能够修理你的傀儡。")
t("Not enough space to refit!", "没有足够的空间改装！")
t([[Take care of your golem:
		- If it is destroyed, you will take some time to reconstruct it (this takes 15 alchemist gems and 20 turns).
		- If it is alive but hurt, you will be able to repair it for %d (takes 2 alchemist gems). Spellpower, alchemist gem and Golem Power talent all influence the healing done.]], [[与你的傀儡进行交互： 
		- 如果它被摧毁，你将耗费一些时间重新安装傀儡（需要 15 个炼金宝石）。 
		- 如果它还存活，你可以修整它使其恢复 %d 生命值。（耗费 2 个炼金宝石）。法术强度、炼金宝石和强化傀儡技能都会影响治疗量。]])
t("Golem Power", "强化傀儡")
t("Improves your golem's proficiency with weapons, increasing its Accuracy by %d, Physical Power by %d and damage by %d%%.", "提高傀儡的武器熟练度，增加它 %d 点命中、 %d 物理强度和 %d%% 伤害。")
t("Golem Resilience", "坚韧傀儡")
t([[Improves your golem's armour training, damage resistance, and healing efficiency.
		Increases all damage resistance by %d%%; increases Armour value by %d, Armour hardiness by %d%%, reduces chance to be critically hit by %d%% when wearing heavy mail or massive plate armour, and increases healing factor by %d%%.
		The golem can always use any kind of armour, including massive armours.]], [[提高傀儡护甲熟练度和伤害抵抗。 
		增加 %d%% 所有伤害抵抗；增加 %d 点护甲和 %d%% 护甲韧性；当装备 1 件锁甲或板甲时，减少 %d%% 被暴击率；增加 %d%% 治疗效果。 
		傀儡可以使用所有类型的护甲，包括板甲。]])
t("Invoke Golem", "傀儡召返")
t("Not enough space to invoke!", "没有足够的空间召唤！")
t("You invoke your golem to your side, granting it a temporary melee power increase of %d for 5 turns.", "你将傀儡拉到你身边，使它暂时性增加 %d 点近战物理强度，持续 5 回合。")
t("Golem Portal", "傀儡传送")
t("Your golem is currently inactive.", "你的傀儡当前尚未被激活。")
t("#Target# focuses on #Source#.", "#Target# 将注意力集中到 #Source#。")
t("Teleport to your golem, while your golem teleports to your location. Your foes will be confused, and those that were attacking you will have a %d%% chance to target your golem instead.", [[使用此技能后，你和傀儡将会交换位置。 
		你的敌人会被混乱，那些之前攻击你的敌人将有 %d%% 概率转而攻击傀儡。]])


