t("Kryl-Feijan", "卡洛·斐济")
t("This huge demon is covered in darkness. The ripped flesh of its \"mother\" still hangs from its sharp claws.", "这只巨大的恶魔被黑暗所包围。它的“母亲”的碎肉仍悬挂在它的利爪上。")
