section "game/modules/tome/data/zones/tannen-tower/zone.lua"

t("The portal brought you to what seems to be a cell in the basement of the tower. You must escape!", "传送门将你送到了这座高塔的一个小房间里。你必须逃离！")
t("As you climb up the steps, you see Tannen standing with his drolem, reading a scrap of parchment.  As he reads, his eyes grow wider, and he starts sweating and pacing back and forth.  When he reaches to stuff it in his pocket, he sees you and jumps back like a startled cat.  \"No!  Not now!  You have no idea what's at stake!\"  He retrieves a fistful of brightly-colored flasks from his robes, and his drolem's eyes glow as it springs to life, metal screeching in an impressive imitation of a roar.", "当你爬上楼梯，你看到泰恩正和他的龙傀儡站在一起，手中拿着一张羊皮纸。在他阅读的时候，他的眉头紧皱，汗如雨下，不断来回踱步着。当他攥起纸条试图放进口袋里的时候，他突然望见了你，如同一只受惊吓的猫一样向后跳了几步。“不！不是现在！你根本不懂，现在是生死攸关的时刻！”他从长袍中拿出一把彩色的小瓶子，身旁龙傀儡站了起来，眼睛放射出光芒，金属的响声如同真龙的吼叫一般，让你印象深刻。")
t("Tannen's Tower", "泰恩之塔")


